quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  4,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  4,1,"logo! apne rab se daro jis ne tum ko aik jaan se peda kya aur usi jaan se is ka jora banaya aur un dono se bohat mard o aurat duniya mein phela diye uss khuda se daro jis ka vaastaa day kar tum aik dosray se apne haq mangte ho, aur rishta o qaraabat ke taluqaat ko bigaarnay se parhaiz karo yaqeen jano ke Allah tum par nigrani kar raha hai"
  4,2,"yatimon ke maal unn ko wapas do, achay maal ko buray maal se nah badal lau, aur unn ke maal apne maal ke sath mila kar nah kha jao, yeh bohat bara gunah hai"
  4,3,"aur agar tum yatimon ke sath be insafi karne se drtay ho to jo aurtain tum ko pasand ayen unn mein se do do, teen teen, chaar chaar se nikah karlo lekin agar tumhe andesha ho ke unn ke sath Adal nah kar sakuu ge to phir aik hi biwi karo ya unn aurton ko zojiat mein lao jo tumahray qabza mein aayi hain, be insafi se bachney ke liye yeh ziyada qareen Sawab hai"
  4,4,"aur aurton ke mohar khush dili ke sath ( farz jantay hue ) ada karo, Albata agar woh khud apni khusi se mohar ka koi hissa tumhe maaf kar den to ussay tum mazay se kha satke ho"
  4,5,"aur apne woh maal jinhein Allah ne tumahray liye qiyam zindagi ka zareya banaya hai, nadaan logon ke hawala nah karo, Albata inhen khanay aur pahannay ke liye do aur inhen naik hadaayat karo"
  4,6,"aur yatimon ki azmaish karte raho yahan taq ke woh nikah ke qabil Umar ko poanch jayen phir agar tum unn ke andar ahliat pao to unn ke maal unn ke hawalay kar do aisa kabhi nah karna ke hadd insaaf se tajawaz kar ke iss khauf se unn ke maal jaldi jaldi kha jao ke woh barray ho kar apne haq ka mutalba karen ge yateem ka jo sarparast maal daar ho woh parhaiz gari se kaam le aur jo ghareeb ho woh Maroof tareeqa se khaye phir jab unn ke maal unn ke hawalay karne lagu to logon ko is par gawah bana lau, aur hisaab lainay ke liye Allah kaafi hai"
  4,7,"mardon ke liye uss maal mein hissa hai jo maa baap aur rishta daaron ne chorra ho, aur aurton ke liye bhi uss maal mein hissa hai jo maa baap aur rishta daaron ne chorra ho, khuwa thora ho ya bohat, aur yeh hissa ( Allah ki taraf se ) muqarrar hai"
  4,8,aur jab taqseem ke mauqa par kunba ke log aur yateem aur maskeen ayen to is maal mein se un ko bhi kuch do aur unn ke sath bhallay manson ki si baat karo
  4,9,logon ko is baat ka khayaal kar ke darna chahiye ke agar woh khud apne peechay be bas aulaad chortay to martay waqt inhen apne bachon ke haq mein kaisay kuch andaishay la-haq hotay pas chahiye ke woh khuda ka khauf karen aur raasti ki baat karen
  4,10,jo log zulm ke sath yatimon ke maal khatay hain Dur haqeeqat woh apne pait aag se bhartay hain aur woh zaroor jahannum ki bharakti hui aag mein jhonkay jayen ge
  4,11,"tumhari aulaad ke baray mein Allah tumhe hadaayat karta hai ke : mard ka hissa do aurton ke barabar hai, agar ( maiyat ki waris ) do se zayed larkiyan hon to inhen trke ka do tahai diya jaye, aur agar aik hi larki waris ho to aadha tarka is ka hai agar maiyat sahib aulaad ho twas ke walidain mein se har aik ko trke ka chhata hissa milna chahiye aur agar woh sahib aulaad nah ho aur walidain hi is ke waris ho n to maa ko teesra hissa diya jaye aur agar maiyat ke bhai behan bhi hon to maa chhatay hissa ki haq daar hogi ( yeh sab hissay uss waqt nikalay jayen ) jabkay wasiyat jo maiyat ne ki ho poori kar di jaye aur qarz jo uss par ho ada kar diya jaye tum nahi jantay ke tumahray maa baap aur tumhari aulaad mein se kon bilhaaz naffa tum se qareeb tar hai yeh hissay Allah ne muqarrar kar diye hain, aur Allah yaqeenan sab haqeeqaton se waaqif aur saari maslehton ka jan-nay wala hai"
  4,12,"aur tumhari biwion ne jo kuch chorra ho is ka aadha hissa tumhe miley ga agar woh be aulaad hon, warna aulaad honay ki soorat mein tarka ka aik chothai hissa tumhara hai jabkay wasiyat jo unhon n ne ki ho poori kar di jaye, aur qarz jo onhon ne chorra ho ada kar diya jaye aur woh tumahray tarka mein se chothai ki haq daar hon gi agar tum be aulaad ho, warna sahib aulaad honay ki soorat mein unn ka hissa aathwan hoga, baad is ke ke jo wasiyat tum ne ki ho woh poori kar di jaye aur jo qarz tum ne chorra ho woh ada kar diya jaye aur agar woh mard ya aurat ( jis ki meeras taqseem talab hai ) be aulaad bhi ho aur is ke maa baap bhi zindah nah hon, magar is ka aik bhai ya aik behan mojood ho to bhai aur behan har aik ko chhata hissa miley ga, aur bhai behan aik se ziyada hon to kal tarka ke aik tahai mein woh sab shareek hon ge, jabkay wasiyat jo ki gayi ho poori kar di jaye, aur qarz jo maiyat ne chorra ho ada kar diya jaye, bashar tik_h woh zarrar rasan nah ho yeh hukum hai Allah ki taraf se aur Allah Dana o Beena aur naram khoo hai"
  4,13,yeh Allah ki muqarrar ki hui hade hain jo Allah aur uss ke rasool ki itaat kere ga ussay Allah aisay baghoon mein daakhil kere ga jin ke neechay nhrin behti hon gi aur un baghoon mein woh hamesha rahay ga aur yahi barri kamyabi hai
  4,14,aur jo Allah aur uss ke rasool ki nafarmani kere ga aur is ki muqarrar ki hui hado se tajawaz kar jaye ga ussay Allah aag mein daaley ga jis mein woh hamesha rahay ga aur is ke liye ruswa kin saza hai
  4,15,"tumhari aurton mein se jo bad kaari ki murtakib hon unn par apne mein se chaar admion ki gawahi lau, aur agar chaar aadmi gawahi day den to un ko gharon mein band rakho yahan taq ke inhen mout aa jaye ya Allah unn ke liye koi rasta nikaal day"
  4,16,"aur tum mein se jo is feal ka irtikaab karen unn dono ko takleef do, phir agar woh tauba karen aur apni islaah kar len to inhen chore do ke Allah bohat tauba qubool karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  4,17,haan yeh jaan lau ke Allah par tauba ki qabuliat ka haq aُnhi logon ke liye hai jo nadani ki wajah se koi bura feal kar guzarte hain aur is ke baad jaldi hi tauba kar letay hain aisay logon par Allah apni nazar inayat se phir mutwajjah ho jata hai aur Allah saari baton ki khabar rakhnay wala aur hakeem o Dana hai
  4,18,"magar tauba unn logon ke liye nahi hai jo buray kaam kiye chalay jatay hain yahan taq ke jab un mein se kisi ki mout waqt aa jata hai uss waqt woh kehta hai ke ab mein ne tauba ki, aur isi terhan tauba unn ke liye bhi nahi hai jo martay dam taq kafir rahen a ‫se logon ke liye to hum ne dard naak saza tayyar kar rakhi hai"
  4,19,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, tumahray liye yeh halal nahi hai ke zabardasti aurton ke waris ban betho aur nah yeh halal hai ke inhen tang kar ke uss mohar ka kuch hissa ura lainay ki koshish karo jo tum inhen day chuke ho haan agar woh kisi Sarih bad chalni ki murtakib ho n ( to zaroor tumhe tang karne ka haq hai ) un ke sath bhallay tareeqa se zindagi busr karo agar woh tumhe napasand hon to ho sakta hai ke aik cheez tumhe pasand nah ho magar Allah ne usi mein bohat kuch bhalai rakh di ho"
  4,20,"aur agar tum aik biwi ki jagah doosri biwi le anay ka iradah hi kar lau to khuwa tum ne ussay dhair sa maal hi kyun nah diya ho, is mein se kuch wapas nah lena kya tum ussay bohtan laga kar aur Sarih zulm kar ke wapas lau ge ?"
  4,21,aur aakhir tum ussay kis terhan le lau ge jab ke tum aik dosray se lutaf andoo zay ho chuke ho aur woh tum se pukhta ehad le chuki hain ?
  4,22,"aur jin aurton se tumahray baap nikah kar chuke hon unn se hargiz nikah nah karo, magar jo pehlay ho chuka so ho chuka Dur haqeeqat yeh aik be hiyai ka feal hai, napasandeedah hai aur bura chalan hai"
  4,23,"tum par haraam ki gayeen tumhari maaen, betiyan, behnain, phophyan, khala-ayn, bhtijyan, bhanjyan, aur tumhari woh maaen jinhon ne tum ko doodh pilaya ho, aur tumhari doodh shareek behnain, aur tumhari biwion ki maaen, aur tumhari biwion ki larkiyan jinhon ne tumhari godoo-nmein parwarish payi hai unn biwion ki larkiyan jin se tumhara talluq zan o show ho chuka ho warna agar ( sirf nikah howa ho aur ) talluq zan o show nah howa ho to ( a nahi chore kar un ki larkiyon se nikah kar lainay mein ) tum par koi muwakhza nahi hai aur tumahray unn beton ki biwiyan jo tumhari Sulb se hon aur yeh bhi tum par haraam kya gaya hai ke aik nikah mein do behnoon ko jama karo, magar jo pehlay ho gaya so ho gaya, Allah bakhsnay wala aur reham karne wala hai"
  4,24,"aur woh aurtain bhi tum par haraam hain jo kisi dosray ke nikah mein hon(mohsnaat) Albata aisi aurtain is se mustasna hain jo ( jung mein ) tumahray haath ayen yeh Allah ka qanoon hai jis ki pabandi tum par lazim kar di gayi hai inn ke masiwa jitni aurtain hain inhen apne amwal ke zareya se haasil karna tumahray liye halal kar diya gaya hai, bashar tik_h hisaar nikah mein unn ko mehfooz karo, nah yeh ke azad shehwat rani karne lagu phir jo azdawaji zindagi ka lutaf tum un se uthao is ke badlay unn ke mohar bator farz ada karo, Albata mohar ki qarardad ho jaane ke baad aapas ki razamandi se tumahray darmain agar koi samjhota ho jaye to is mein koi harj nahi, Allah Aleem aur Dana hai"
  4,25,"aur jo shakhs tum mein se itni mqdrt nah rakhta ho ke khandani musalman aurton(mohsnaat) se nikah kar sakay usay chahiye ke tumhari unn londion mein se kisi ke sath nikah kar le jo tumahray qabza mein hon aur Momina hon Allah tumahray imanoon ka haal khoob jaanta hai, tum sab aik hi giroh ke log ho, lehaza unn ke srprston ki ijazat se unn ke sath nikah kar lau aur Maroof tareeqa se unn ke mohar ada kar do, taakay woh hisaar nikah mein mehfooz(mohsnaat) ho kar rahen, azad shehwat rani karti phrin aur nah chori chupay آ(ashnaiya-nkaren phir jab woh hisaar nikah mein mehfooz ho jayen aur is ke baad kisi bad chalni ki murtakib hon to un par uss sz a ki bah nisbat aadhi saza hai jo khandani aurton(mohsnaat) ke liye muqarrar hai yeh sahoolat tum mein se unn logon ke liye peda ki gayi hai jin ko shadi nah karne se band taqwa ke toot jaane ka andesha ho lekin agar tum sabr karo to yeh tumahray liye behtar hai, aur Allah bakhsnay wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  4,26,"Allah chahta hai ke tum par unn tareeqon ko wazeh kere aur unhi tareeqon par tumhe chalaye jin ki pairwi tum se pehlay guzray hueSullhaa karte thay woh apni rehmat ke sath tumhari taraf mutwajjah honay ka iradah rakhta hai, aur woh Aleem bhi hai aur Dana bhi"
  4,27,"haan, Allah to tum par rehmat ke sath tavajja karna chahta hai magar jo log khud apni khwahisaat nafs ki pairwi kar rahay hain woh chahtay hain ke tum raah raast se hatt kar daur nikal jao"
  4,28,Allah tum par se pabandion ko halka karna chahta hai kyunkay ensaan kamzor peda kya gaya hai
  4,29,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, aapas mein aik dosray ke maal baatil tareeqon se nah khao, lain deen hona chahiye aapas ki razamandi se aur apne aap ko qatal nah karo yaqeen manu ke Allah tumahray oopar meharban hai"
  4,30,jo shakhs zulm o zayad-ti ke sath aisa kere ga uss ko hum zaroor aag mein jhonkainge aur yeh Allah ke liye koi mushkil kaam nahi hai
  4,31,agar tum unn barray barray gunaaho se parhaiz karte raho jin se tumhe mana kya ja raha hai to tumhari choti mouti buraiyon ko hum tumahray hisaab se saqt kar den ge aur tum ko izzat ki jagah daakhil karen ge
  4,32,"aur jo kuch Allah ne tum mein se kisi ko dosaron ke muqaabla mein ziyada diya hai is ki tamanna nah karo jo kuch Mardon ne kamaya hai uss ke mutabiq un ka hissa hai aur jo kuch aurton ne kamaya hai is ke mutabiq unn ka hissa haan Allah se is ke fazl ki dua mangte raho, yaqeenan Allah har cheez ka ilm rakhta hai"
  4,33,"aur hum ne har uss trke ke haq daar muqarrar kar diye hain jo walidain aur rishta daar choden ab rahay woh log jin se tumahray ehad o Paiman hon to un ka hissa inhen do, yaqeenan Allah har cheez par nigaran hai"
  4,34,"mard aurton par qiwaam hain, is bana par ke Allah ne unn mein se aik ko dosray par fazeelat di hai, aur is bana par ke mard apne maal kharch karte hain pas jo Saleh aurtain hain woh itaat shoaar hoti hain aur mardon ke peechay Allah ki hifazat o nigrani mein unn ke haqooq ki hifazat karti hain aur jin aurton se tumhe sar kashi ka andesha ho inhen samjhao, khawab gaahon mein unn se alehda raho aur maro, phir agar tum woh tumhari Mutee ho jayen to khuwa makhuwa un par dast Darazi ke liye bahanay talaash nah karo, yaqeen rakho ke oopar Allah mojood hai jo bara aur baala tar hai"
  4,35,"aur agar tum logon ko kahin miyan aur biwi ke taluqaat baggar jaane ka andesha ho to aik hukum mard ke rishta daaron mein se aur aik aurat ke rishta daaron mein se muqarrar karo, woh dono islaah karna chahain ge to Allah unn ke darmain muwafiqat ki soorat nikaal day ga, Allah sab kuch jaanta hai aur bakhabar hai"
  4,36,"aur tum sab Allah ki bandagi karo, uss ke sath kisi ko shareek nah banaao, maa baap ke sath naik bartao karo, qaraabat daaron aur yatimon aur miskeeno ke sath husn sulooq se paish aao, aur parosi rishta daar se, ajnabi hamsaaya se, pehlu ke saathi aur musafir se, aur unn londi ghulamoo se jo tumahray qabza mein hon, ahsaan ka maamla rakho, yaqeen jano Allah kisi aisay shakhs ko pasand nahi karta jo apne Pindar mein maghrour ho aur apni barayi par fakhr kar y"
  4,37,aur aisay log bhi Allah ko pasand nahi hain jo kanjoosi karte hain aur dosaron ko bhi kanjoosi ki hadaayat karte hain aur jo kuch Allah ne apne fazl se inhen diya hai usay chupatay hain aisay kafir Nemat logon ke liye hum ne ruswa kin azaab muhayya kar rakha hai
  4,38,aur woh log bhi Allah ko napasand hain jo apne maal mehez logon ko dikhaane keliye kharch karte hain aur Dur haqeeqat nah Allah par imaan rakhtay hain nah roz aakhir par sach yeh hai ke shetan jis ka Rafeeq howa ussay bohat hi buri rafaqat muyassar aayi
  4,39,aakhir inn logon par kya aafat aa jati agar yeh Allah aur roz aakhir par imaan rakhtay aur jo kuch Allah ne diya hai is mein se kharch karte agar yeh aisa karte to Allah se un ki neki ka haal chhupa nah reh jata
  4,40,Allah kisi par zarra barabar bhi zulm nahi karta agar koi aik neki kere to Allah ussay do chand karta hai aur phir apni taraf se bara ajar ataa farmata hai
  4,41,phir socho ke uss waqt yeh kya karen ge jab hum har ummat mein se aik gawah layein ge aur inn logon par tumhe ( yani Mohammad ko ) gawah ki hesiyat se khara karen ge
  4,42,"uss waqt woh sab log jinhon ne Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki baat nah maani aur is ki nafarmani karte rahay, tamanna karen ge ke kash zameen phatt jaye aur woh is mein sama jayen wahan yeh apni koi baat Allah se nah chhupa saken ge"
  4,43,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jab tum nashay ki haalat mein ho to namaz ke qareeb nah jao namaz uss waqt padni chahiye, jab tum jano ke kya keh rahay ho aur isi terhan janabat ki haalat mein bhi namaz ke qareeb nah jao jab taq ke ghusal nah kar lau, ila yeh ke rasta se guzarte ho aur agar kabhi aisa ho ke tum bemaar ho, ya safar mein ho, ya tum mein se koi shakhs rafa haajat kar ke aeye, ya tum ne aurton se lams kya ho, aur phir pani nah miley to pak matti se kaam lau aur is se apne cheharon aur hathon par maseh kar lau, be shak Allah narmi se kaam lainay wala aur bakhshish frmane wala hai"
  4,44,tum ne unn logon ko bhi dekha jinhein kitaab ke ilm ka kuch hissa diya gaya hai? woh khud zallatke khredar banay hue hain aur chahtay hain ke tum bhi raah gum kar do
  4,45,Allah tumahray dushmanon ko khoob jaanta hai aur tumhari himayat o madad gari ke liye Allah hi kaafi hai
  4,46,jo log yahodi ban gay hain unn mein kuch log hain jo alfaaz ko unn ke mehal se phair dete hain aur deen haq ke khilaaf naysh zani karne ke liye apni zabanon ko toar mourr kar kehte hain sami'naa wa 'asainaaaur asma' ghaira musma'inw aurraa'inaahalaank agar woh kehtesami'naa wa ata'naaaur asma' aur anzurnaa tu yeh unhi ke liye behtar tha aur ziyada rastbazika tareeqa tha magar un par to un ki baatil parasti ki badolat Allah ki phatkaar pari hui hai is liye woh kam hi imaan laatay hain
  4,47,"ae woh logo jinhein kitaab di gayi thi! maan lau uss kitaab ko jo hum ne ab nazil ki hai aur jo uss kitaab ki tasdeeq o taied karti hai jo tumahray paas pehlay se mojood thi is par imaan le aao qabal is ke ke hum ch_hr y bigaar kar peechay phair den ya un ko isi terhan laanat zada kar den jis terhan sabt walon ke sath hum ne kya tha, aur yaad rakho ke Allah ka hukum nafiz ho kar rehta hai"
  4,48,"Allah bas shirk hi ko maaf nahi karta, iss ke masiwa dosray jis qader gunah hain woh jis ke liye chahta hai maaf kar deta hai Allah ke sath jis ne kisi aur ko shareekTehraya uss ne to bohat hi bara jhoot tasneef kya aur barray sakht gunah ki baat ki"
  4,49,"tum ne unn logon ko bhi dekha jo bohat apni pakeezgi nafs ka dam bhartay hain? halaank pakizgee to Allah hi jisay chahta hai ataa karta hai, aur ( inhen jo pakizgee nahi millti to Dur haqeeqat ) un par zarra barabar bhi zulm nahi kya jata"
  4,50,"dekho to sahi, yeh Allah par bhi jhutay aftara gharnay se nahi chokte aur un ke srihan gunah ga ray honay ke liye yahi aik gunah kaafi hai"
  4,51,kya tum ne unn logon ko nahi dekha jinhein kitaab ke ilm mein se kuch hissa diya gaya hai aur unn ka haal yeh hai ke جبت aur Taghoot ko mantay hain aur kafiroon ke mutaliq kehte hain ke imaan laane walon se to yahi ziyada sahih rastay par hain
  4,52,aisay hi log hain jin par Allah ne laanat ki hai aur jis par Allah laanat kar day phir tum uss ka koi madad gaar nahi pao ge
  4,53,kya hukoomat mein unn ka koi hissa hai? agar aisa hota to yeh dosaron ko aik phooty kori taq nah dete
  4,54,phir kya yeh dosaron se is liye hasad karte hain ke Allah ne inhen apne fazl se Nawaz diya? agar yeh baat hai to inhen maloom ho ke hum ne to ibrahim ki aulaad ko kitaab aur hikmat ataa ki aur malik azeem bakhash diya
  4,55,"magar un mein se koi is par imaan laya aur koi is se mun mourr gaya, aur mun mourr ne walon ke liye to bas jahannum ki bharakti hui aag hi kaafi hai"
  4,56,"jin logon ne hamari ayaat ko maan-ne se inkaar kar diya hai inhen bilyaqeenhum aag mein jhonkainge aur jab un ke badan ki khaal Gul jaye gi to is ki jagah doosri khaal peda kar den ge taakay woh khoob azaab ka maza chakhain, Allah barri qudrat rakhta hai aur apne faislon ko amal mein laane ki hikmat khoob jaanta hai"
  4,57,"aur jin logon ne hamari ayaat ko maan liya aur naik amal kiye unn ko hum aisay baghoon mein daakhil karen ge jin ke neechay nhrin behti hon gi, jahan woh hamesha hamesha rahen ge aur unn ko pakeeza biwiyan milein gi aur inhen hum ghani chaon mein rakhen ge"
  4,58,"mslmano! Allah tumhe hukum deta hai ke amanatain ahal amanat ke supurd karo, aur jab logon ke darmain faisla karo to Adal ke sath karo, Allah tum ko nihayat umdah nasiyaat karta hai aur yaqeenan Allah sab kuch santa aur daikhta hai"
  4,59,"ae logo jo imaan laaye hue, itaat karo Allah ki aur itaat karo rasool ki aur unn logon ki jo tum mein se sahib amar hon, phir agar tumahray darmain kisi maamla mein nazaa ho jaye to usay Allah aur rasool ki taraf phair do agar tum waqai Allah aur roz aakhir par imaan rakhtay ho yahi aik sahih tareeq car hai aur injaam ke aitbaar se bhi behtar hai"
  4,60,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! tum ne dekha nahi unn logon ko jo daawa to karte hain ke hum imaan laaye hain uss kitaab par jo tumhari taraf nazil ki gayi hai aur un kitabon par jo tum se pehlay nazil ki gayi theen, magar chahtay yeh hain ke apne mamlaat ka faisla karanay ke liye Taghoot ki taraf rujoo karen, halaank inhen Taghoot se kufar karne ka hukum diya gaya tha shetan inhen bhatka kar raah raast se bohat daur le jana chahta hai"
  4,61,aur jab un se kaha jata hai ke aao uss cheez ki taraf jo Allah ne nazil ki hai aur aao rasool ki taraf to un mnafqon ko tum dekhte ho ke yeh tumhari taraf anay se qatrate hain
  4,62,phir is waqt kya hota hai jab inn ke apne hathon ki layi hui museebat un par aa padtee hai? uss waqt yeh tumahray paas kasmain khatay hue atay hain aur kehte hain ke khuda ki qasam hum to sirf bhalai chahtay thay aur hamari niyat to yeh thi ke fariqain mein kisi terhan muwafiqat ho jaye
  4,63,"Allah jaanta hai jo kuch un ke dilon mein hai, un se tarruz mat karo, inhen samjhao aur aisi nasiyaat karo jo un ke dilon mein utar jaye"
  4,64,"( inhen batao ke ) hum ne jo rasool bhi bheja hai is liye bheja hai ke azan khuda wandi ki bana par is ki itaat ki jaye agar unhon ne yeh tareeqa ikhtiyar kya hota ke jab yeh apne nafs par zulm kar baithy thay to tumahray paas aa jatay aur Allah se maffi mangte, aur rasool bhi un ke liye maffi ki darkhwast karta, to yaqeenan Allah ko bakhsnay wala aur reham karne wala paate"
  4,65,"nahi, ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tumahray rab ki qasam yeh kabhi momin nahi ho saktay jab taq ke apne bahami ikhtilafat mein yeh tum ko faisla karne wala nah maan len, phir jo kuch tum faisla karo is par apne dilon mein bhi koi tangi nah mehsoos karen, balkay sir busr tasleem kar len"
  4,66,"agar hum ne inhen hukum diya hota ke apne aap ko halaak kar do ya apne gharon se nikal jao to un mein se kam hi aadmi is par amal karte halaank jo nasiyaat inhen ki jati hai, agar yeh is par amal karte to yeh un ke liye ziyada behtari aur ziyada saabit qadmi ka mojab hota"
  4,67,aur jab yeh aisa karte to hum inhen apni taraf se bohat bara ajar dete
  4,68,aur inhen seedha rasta dikha dete
  4,69,jo Allah aur rasool ki ita'at kere ga woh un logon ke sath hoga jin par Allah ne inaam farmaya hai yani anbiyaa aur siddiqeenaur shuhdaa ٫ aur saliheen kaisay achay hain yeh Rafeeq jo kisi ko muyassar ayen
  4,70,yeh haqeeqi fazl hai jo Allah ki taraf se milta hai aur haqeeqat jan-nay ke liye bas Allah hi ka ilm kaafi hai
  4,71,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, muqaabla ke liye har waqt tayyar raho, phir jaissa mauqa ho allag allag daston ki shakal mein niklo ya ikathay ho kar"
  4,72,"haan, tum mein koi aadmi aisa bhi hai jo larai se jee churata hai, a gir tum par koi museebat aeye to kehta hai ke Allah ne mujh par bara fazl kya ke mein inn logon ke sath nah gaya"
  4,73,aur agar Allah ki taraf se tum par fazl ho to kehta hai aur is terhan kehta hai ke goya tumahray aur is ke darmain mohabbat ka to koi talluq tha hi nahi ke kash mein bhi un ke sath hota to bara kaam ban jata
  4,74,"( aisay logon ko maloom ho ke ) Allah ki raah mein larna chahiye unn logon ko jo akhirat ke badlay duniya ki zindagi ko farokht kar den, phir jo Allah ki raah mein larray ga aur mara jaye ga ya ghalib rahay ga ussay zaroor hum ajar azeem ataa karen ge"
  4,75,"aakhir kya wajah hai ke tum Allah ki raah mein unn be bas mardon, aurton aur bachon ki khatir nah lrho jo kamzor paker daba liye gay hain aur faryaad kar rahay hain ke khudaaya hum ko is bastii se nikaal jis ke bashinday zalim hain aur apni taraf se hamara koi haami o madad gaar peda kar day"
  4,76,"jin logon ne imaan ka rasta ikhtiyar kya hai, woh Allah ki raah mein lartay hain aur jinhon ne kufar ka rasta ikhtiyar kya hai, o hay Taghoot ki raah mein lartay hain, pas shetan ke sathiyon se lrho aur yaqeen jano ke shetan ki chaalein haqeeqat mein nihayat kamzor hain"
  4,77,"tum ne unn logon ko bhi dekha jin se kaha gaya tha ke apne haath rokay rakho aur namaz qaim karo aur zkoh do? ab jo inhen larai ka hukum diya gaya to un mein se aik fareeq ka haal yeh hai ke logon se aisa dar rahay hain jaissa khuda se darna chahiye ya kuch is se bhi barh kar kehte hain khudaaya! yeh hum par larai ka hukum kyun likh diya? kyun nah hamein abhi kuch aur mohlat di? un se kaho, duniya ka sarmaya zindagi thora hai, aur akhirat aik khuda taras ensaan ke liye ziyada behtar hai, aur tum par zulm aik Shamah barabar bhi nah kya jaye ga"
  4,78,"rahi mout, to jahan bhi tum ho woh behar haal tumhe aakar rahay gi khuwa tum kaisi hi mazboot imaarton mein ho agar inhen koi faida pohanchana hai to kehte hain yeh Allah ki taraf se hai, aur agar koi nuqsaan pohanchana hai to kehte hain yeh tumhari badolat hai kaho, sab kuch Allah hi ki taraf se hai aakhir un logon ko kya ho gaya hai ke koi baat un ki samajh mein nahi aati"
  4,79,"ae ensaan! tujhe jo bhalai bhi haasil hoti hai Allah ki inayat se hoti hai, aur jo museebat tujh par aati hai woh tairay apne ksb o amal ki badolat hai ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! hum ne tum ko logon ke liye rasool bana kar bheja hai aur iss par khuda ki gawahi kaafi hai"
  4,80,"jis ne rasool ki itaat ki is ne darasal khuda ki itaat ki aur jo mun mourr gaya, to behar haal hum ne tumhe un logon par Pasban bana kar to nahi bheja hai"
  4,81,"woh mun par kehte hain ke hum Mutee farmaan hain magar jab tumahray paas se nikaltay hain to un mein se aik giroh raton ko jama ho kar tumhari baton ke khilaaf mashwaray karta hai Allah un ki yeh saari sargoshian likh raha hai tum un ki parwa nah karo aur Allah par bharosa rakho, wohi bharosa ke liye kaafi hai"
  4,82,kya yeh log quran par ghhor nahi karte? agar yeh Allah ke siwa kisi aur ki taraf se hota to iss mein bohat kuch ikhtilaaf bayani payi jati
  4,83,"yeh log jahan koi itminan bakhash ya khofnaak khabar sun paate hain ussay le kar phela dete hain, halaank agar yeh ussay rasool aur apni jamaat ke zimma daar ashaab taq p_hnchayin to woh aisay logon ke ilm mein aa jaye jo inn ke darmain is baat ki salahiyat rakhtay hain ke is se sahih nateeja akhaz kar saken tum logon par Allah ki meharbani aur rehmat nah hoti to ( tumhari kmzoryan aisi theen ke ) madode chand ke siwa tum sab shetan ke peechay lag gay hotay"
  4,84,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! tum Allah ki raah mein lrho, tum apni zaat ke siwa kisi aur ke liye zimma daar nahi ho Albata ahal aima noon ko larnay ke liye uksao, baeed nahi ke Allah kafiroon ka zor toar day, Allah ka zor sab se ziyada zabardast aur is ki saza sab se ziyada sakht hai"
  4,85,"jo bhalai ki sifarish karega woh is mein se hissa paye ga aur jo buraiee ki sifarish kere ga woh is mein se hissa paye ga, aur Allah har cheez par nazar rakhnay wala hai"
  4,86,"aur jab koi ehtram ke sath tumhe salam kere to is ko is se behtar tareeqa ke sath jawab do ya kam az kam usi terhan, Allah har cheez ka hisaab lainay wala hai"
  4,87,"Allah woh hai jis ke siwa koi khuda nahi hai, woh tum sab ko uss qayamat ke din jama kere ga jis ke anay mein koi shb_hh nahi, aur Allah ki baat se barh kar sachhi baat aur kis ki hosakti hai"
  4,88,"phir yeh tumhe kya ho gaya hai ke munafiqeen ke baray mein tumahray darmain do rayein payi jati hain, halaank jo buraiyan onhon ne kamaai hain unn ki badolat Allah inhen ulta phair chuka hai kya tum chahtay ho ke jisay Allah ne hadaayat nahi bakhsh ussay tum hadaayat bakhash do? halaank jis ko Allah ne rasta se hata diya uss ke liye tum koi rasta nahi paskte"
  4,89,"woh to yeh chahtay hain ke jis terhan woh khud kafir hain isi terhan tum bhi kafir ho jao taakay tum aur woh sab yaksaa ho jayen lehaza un mein se kisi ko apna dost nah banaao jab taq ke woh Allah ki raah mein hijrat kar ke nah aa jayen, aur agar woh hijrat se baz rahen to jahan pao inhen pakro aur qatal karo aur un mein se kisi ko apna dost aur madadgaar nah banaao"
  4,90,"Albata o hay munafiq is hukum se mustasna hain jo kisi aisi qoum se ja milein jis ke sath tumhara moahida hai isi terhan woh munafiq bhi mustasna hain jo tumahray paas atay hain aur larai se dil bardashta hain, nah tum se larna chahtay hain nah apni qoum se Allah chahta to un ko tum par musallat kar deta aur woh bhi tum se lartay lehaza agar woh tum se kinara kash ho jayen aur larnay se baz rahen aur tumhari taraf sulah o aashtee ka haath barhayain to Allah ne tumahray liye un par dast Darazi ki koi Sabeel nahi rakhi hai"
  4,91,"aik aur qisam ke munafiq tumhe aisay milein ge jo chahtay hain ke tum se bhi aman mein rahen aur apni qoum se bhi, magar jab kabhi fitnah ka mauqa payen ge is mein kood parrin ge aisay log agar tumahray muqaabla se baz nah rahen aur sulah o salamti tumahray agay paish nah karen aur apne haath nah rokain to jahan woh milein inhen pakro aur maro, un par haath uthany ke liye hum ne tumhe khuli Hujjat day di hai"
  4,92,"kisi momin ka yeh kaam nahi hai ke dosray momin ko qatal kere, ila yeh ke uss se chowk ho jaye, aur jo shakhs kisi momin ko ghalti se qatal kar day to is ka kaffara yeh hai ke aik momin ko ghulami se azad kere aur maqtool ke varson ko khoon baha day, ila yeh ke woh khoon baha maaf kar den lekin agar woh musalman maqtool kisi aisi qoum se tha jis se tumhari dushmani ho to is ka kaffara aik momin ghulam azad karna hai aur agar woh kisi aisi ghirmslm qoum ka fard tha jis se tumhara moahida ho to is ke varson ko khoon baha diya jaye ga aur aik momin ghulam ko azad karna hoga phir jo ghulam nah paye woh pay Dur pay do mahinay ke rozay rakhay yeh iss gunah par Allah se tauba karne ka tareeqa hai aur Allah Aleem o Dana hai"
  4,93,raha woh shakhs jo kisi momin ko jaan boojh kar qatal kere to uss ki jaza jahannum hai jis mein woh hamesha rahay ga is par Allah ka ghazab aur uss ki laanat hai aur Allah ne is ke liye sakht azaab muhayya kar rakha hai
  4,94,"ae logo jo aima noon laaye ho, jab tum Allah ki raah mein jehaad ke liye niklo to dost dushman mein tameez karo aur jo tumhari taraf salam se taqdeem kere ussay foran nah keh do ke to momin nahi hai agar tum dunewi faida chahtay ho to Allah ke paas tumahray liye bohat se amwal ghanemat hain aakhir isi haalat mein tum khud bhi to is se pehlay mubtala reh chuke ho, phir Allah ne tum par ahsaan kya, lehaza tahaqeeq se kaam lau, jo kuch tum karte ho Allah uss se bakhabar hai"
  4,95,"musalmanoon mein se woh log jo kisi mazoori ke baghair ghar baithy rehtay hain aur woh jo Allah ki raah mein jaan o maal se jehaad karte hain, dono ki hesiyat yaksaa nahi hai Allah ne bethnay walon ki bah nisbat jaan o maal se jehaad karne walon ka darja bara rakha hai agarchay har aik ke liye Allah ne bhalai hi ka wada farmaya hai, magar uss ke haan mjahdon ki khidmaat ka muawza bethnay walon se bohat ziyada hai"
  4,96,"unn ke liye Allah ki taraf se barray darjay hain aur mughfirat aur rehmat hai, aur Allah bara maaf karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  4,97,"jo log apne nafs par zulm kar rahay thay unn ki roohein jab firshton ne qabz kee to un se poocha ke yeh tum kis haal mein mubtala thay? unhon ne jawab diya ke hum zameen mein kamzor o majaboor thay firshton ne kaha, kya khuda ki zameen wasee nah thi ke tum is mein hijrat karte? yeh woh log hain jin ka thikana jahannum hai aur bara hi bura thikana hai"
  4,98,"haan jo mard, aurtain aur bachay waqai be bas hain aur niklny ka koi rasta aur zareya nahi paate"
  4,99,"baeed nahi ke Allah inhen maaf kar day, Allah bara maaf karne wala aur dar guzar frmane wala hai"
  4,100,"jo koi Allah ki raah mein hijrat kere ga woh zameen mein panah lainay ke liye bohat jagah aur basarauqaat ke liye barri gunjaish paye ga, aur jo apne ghar se Allah aur rasool ki taraf hijrat ke liye niklay, phir rasta hi mein ussay mout aa jaye uss ka ajar Allah ke zimmay wajib ho gaya, Allah bohat bakhshish frmane wala aur Raheem hai"
  4,101,aur jab tum log safar ke liye niklo to koi muzahiqa nahi agar namaz mein ikhtisaar kar do ( khasosan ) jabkay tumhe andesha ho ke kafir tumhe satain ge kyunkay woh khullam khula tumhari dushmani par taley hue hain
  4,102,"aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! jab tum musalmanoon ke darmain ho aur ( haalat jung mein ) inhen namaz parhanay kharray ho to chahiye ke un mein se aik giroh tumahray sath khara ho aur asleha liye rahay, phir jab woh sajda kar le to peechay chala jaye aur dosra giroh jis ne abhi namaz nahi parhi hai aakar tumahray sath parhay aur woh bhi chokanna rahay aur apne asleha liye rahay, kyun ke kufar iss taak mein hain ke tum apne hathyaaron aur apne samaan ki taraf se zara ghaafil ho to woh tum par yakbargitoot parrin Albata agar tum barish ki wajah se takleef mehsoos karo ya bemaar ho to asleha rakh dainay mein koi muzahiqa nahi, magar phir bhi chokannay raho yaqeen rakho ke Allah ne kafiroon ke liye ruswa kin azaab muhayya kar rakha hai"
  4,103,"phir jab namaz se farigh ho jao to kharray aur baithy aur letey, har haal mein Allah ko yaad karte raho aur jab itminan naseeb ho jaye to poori namaz parho numa zay Dur haqeeqat aisa farz hai jo pabandi waqt ke sath ahal imaan par lazim kya gaya hai"
  4,104,iss giroh ke taqub mein kamzoree nah dikhao agar tum takleef utha rahay ho to tumhari terhan woh bhi takleef utha rahay hain aur tum Allah se uss cheez ke umeed waar ho jis ke woh umeed waar nahi hain Allah sab kuch jaanta hai aur woh hakeem o Dana hai
  4,105,ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! hum ne yeh kitaab haq ke sath tumhari taraf nazil ki hai taakay jo raah raast Allah ne tumhe dikhayi hai is ke mutabiq logon ke darmain faisla karo tum bad Dayanat logon ki taraf se jhagrnay walay nah bano
  4,106,"aur Allah se Dur guzar ki darkhwast karo, woh bara dar guzar frmane wala aur Raheem hai"
  4,107,jo lau g apne nafs se khayanat karte hain tum unn ki himayat nah karo Allah ko aisa shakhs pasand nahi hai jo khayanat car aur masiat pesha ho
  4,108,yeh lau g insanon se apni harkaat chhupa satke hain magar khuda se nahi chhupa satke woh to uss waqt bhi unn ke sath hota hai jab yeh raton ko choup kar uss ki marzi ke khilaaf mashwaray karte hain inn ke saaray aamaal par Allah muheet hai
  4,109,"haan! tum logon ne inn mujrimon ki taraf se duniya ki zindagi mein to jhagra kar liya, magar qayamat ke roz un ki taraf se kon jhagra kere ga? aakhir wahan kon inn ka wakeel hoga ?"
  4,110,agar koi shakhs bura feal kar guzray ya apne nafs par zulm kar jaye aur is ke baad Allah se dar guzar ki darkhwast kere to Allah ko dar guzar karne wala aur Raheem paye ga
  4,111,"magar jo buraiee kama le to is ki yeh kamaai usi ke liye wabaal hogi, Allah ko sab baton ki khabar hai aur woh hakeem o Dana hai"
  4,112,phir jis ne koi khata ya gunah kar ke is ka ilzaam kisi be gunah par thop diya uss ne to barray bohtan aur Sarih gunah ka baar samaitt liya
  4,113,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! agar Allah ka fazl tum par nah hota aur is ki rehmat tumahray shaamil haal nah hoti to un mein se aik giroh ne to tumhe ghalat fehmi mein mubtala karne ka faisla kar hi liya tha, halan ke Dur haqeeqat woh khud apne siwa kisi ko ghalat fehmi mein mubtala nahi kar rahay thay aur tumhara koi nuqsaan nah kar saktay thay Allah ne tum par kitaab aur hikmat nazil ki hai aur tum ko woh kuch bataya hai jo tumhe maloom nah tha aur is ka fazl tum par bohat hai"
  4,114,"logon ki khufia sargoshiyon mein aksar o beshtar koi bhalai nahi hoti haan agar koi posheeda tor par sadqa o khairaat ki Talqeen kere ya kisi naik kaam ke liye ya logon ke mamlaat mein islaah karne ke liye kisi se kuch kahe to yeh Albata bhali baat hai, aur jo koi Allah ki Raza joi ke liye aisa kere ga ussay hum bara ajar ataa karen ge"
  4,115,"magar jo shakhs rasool ki mukhalfat par kamar basta ho aur ahal imaan ki rawish ke siwa kisi aur rawish par chalay,dar-aa-n hala-n kehہ is par raah raast wazeh ho chuki ho, to uss ko hum usi taraf chalayein ge jidhar woh khud phir gaya aur usay jahannum mein jhonkainge jo bad tareen jaye qarar hai"
  4,116,"Allah ke haan bas shirk hi ki bakhshish nahi hai, is ke siwa aur sab kuch maaf ho sakta hai jisay woh maaf karna chahay jis ne Allah ke sath kisi ko shareek ٹ Tehrayawoh to gumraahi mein bohat daur nikal gaya"
  4,117,woh Allah ko chore kar deviyon ko mabood banatay hain woh uss baaghi shetan ko mabood banatay hain
  4,118,"jis ko Allah ne laanat zada kya hai ( woh uss shetan ki itaat kar rahay hain ) jis ne Allah se kaha tha ke"" mein tairay bundon se aik muqarrar hissa le kar rahon ga"
  4,119,"mein inhen behka-uon ga, mein inhen aarzouon mein uljhauonga, mein inhen hukum dun ga aur woh mere hukum se janwaron ke kaan pharhin ge aur mein inhen hukum dun ga aur woh mere hukum se khudai saakht mein radd o badal karen ge"" is shetan kojs ne Allah ke bajaye apna walii o sarparast bana liya woh Sarih nuqsaan mein par gaya"
  4,120,"woh inn logon se wada karta hai aur inhen umeeden dilaata hai, magar shetan ke saaray waday bajuz fraib ke aur kuch nahi hain"
  4,121,inn logon ka thikana jahannum hai jis se khulasi ki koi soorat yeh nah payen ge
  4,122,"rahay woh log jo imaan le ayen aur naik amal karen, tawa nahi hum aisay baghoon mein daakhil karen ge jin ke neechay nhrin behti hon gi aur woh wahan hamesha hamesha rahen ge yeh Allah ka sacha wada hai aur Allah se barh kar kon apni baat mein sacha hoga"
  4,123,injaam car nah tumhari aarzouon par moqoof hai nah ahal kitaab ki aarzouon par jo bhi buraiee kere ga is ka phal paye ga aur Allah ke muqaabla mein apne liye koi haami o madad gaar nah paske ga
  4,124,"aur jo naik amal kere ga, khuwa mard ho ya aurat, bashar tik_h ho woh momin, to aisay hi log jannat mein daakhil hon ge aur unn ki zarra barabar haq talfi nah honay paye gi"
  4,125,"uss shakhs se behtar aur kis ka tareeq zindagi ho sakta hai jis ne Allah ke agay sir tasleem khham kar diya aur apna rawayya naik rakha aur yaksu ho kar ibrahim ke tareeqay ki pairwi ki, uss ibrahim ke tareeqay ki jisay Allah ne apna dost bana liya tha"
  4,126,asmano aur zameen mein jo kuch hai Allah ka hai aur Allah har cheez par muheet hai
  4,127,"lau g tum se aurton ke maamla mein Fatwa puchhte hain kaho Allah tumhe unn ke maamla mein Fatwa deta hai, aur sath hi woh ehkaam bhi yaad dilaata hai jo pehlay se tum ko is kitaab mein sunaye ja rahay hain yani woh ehkaam jo unn yateem larkiyon ke mutaliq hain jin ke haq tum ada nahi karte aur jin ke nikah karne se tum baz rehtay ho ( ya lalach ki bana par tum khud un se nikah kar lena chahtay ho ), o ray woh ehkaam jo unn bachon ke mutaliq hain jo becharay koi zor nahi rakhtay Allah tumhe hadaayat karta hai ke yatimon ke sath insaaf par qaim raho, aur jo bhalai tum karo ge woh Allah ke ilm se chhupi nah reh jaye gi"
  4,128,"jab kisi aurat ko apne shohar se bud sulooki ya be rukhi ka khatar hay ho to koi muzahiqa nahi agar miyan aur biwi ( kuch haqooq ki kami Beshi par ) aapas mein sulah kar len sulah bahar haal behtar hai nafs tang dili ke taraf jaldi mael ho jatay hain, lekin agar tum log ahsaan se paish aao aur khuda tarsi se kaam lau to yaqeen rakho ke Allah tumahray is tarz amal se be khabar nah hoga"
  4,129,biwion ke darmain poora poora Adal karna tumahray bas mein nahi hai tum chaho bhi to is par Qadir nahi ho saktay lehaza ( qanoon Ellahi ka Mansha poora karne ke liye yeh kaafi hai ke ) aik biwi ki taraf iss terhan nah jhuk jao ke doosri ko idhar latakta chore do agar tum apna tarz amal durust rakho aur Allah se drtay raho to Allah chasham poshi karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai
  4,130,lekin agar zojin aik dosray se allag hi ho jayen to Allah apni wasee qudrat se har aik ko dosray ki mohtaji se be niaz kar day ga Allah ka daman bohat kushadah hai aur woh Dana o Beena hai
  4,131,"asmano aur zameen mein jo kuch hai sab Allah hi ka hai tum se pehlay jin ko hum ne kitaab di thi inhen bhi yahi hadaayat ki thi aur ab tum ko bhi yahi hadaayat karte hain ke khuda se drtay hue kaam karo lekin agar tum nahi mantay to nah manu, aasman o zameen ki saari cheezon ka maalik Allah hi hai aur woh be niaz hai, har tareef ka mustahiq"
  4,132,"haan Allah hi maalik hai un sab cheezon kajoo asmano mein hain aur jo zameen mein hain, aur car saazi ke liye bas o hi kaafi hai"
  4,133,"agar woh chahay to tum logon ko hata kar tumhari jagah dosaron ko le aeye, aur woh iss ki poori qudrat rakhta hai"
  4,134,"jo shakhs mehez sawab duniya ka taalib ho ussay maloom hona chahiye ke Allah ke paas sawab duniya bhi hai aur sawab akhirat bhi, aur Allah Sami o Baseer hai"
  4,135,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, insaaf ke alambardar aur khuda wastay ke gawah bano agarchay tumahray insaaf aur tumhari gawahi ki zad khud tumhari apni zaat par ya tumahray walidain aur rishta daaron par hi kyun nah padtee ho fareeq maamla khuwa maldaar ho ya ghareeb, Allah tum se ziyada unn ka kher khuwa hai lehaza apni khwahish nafs ki pairwi mein Adal se baz nah raho aur agar tum ne lagi lipti baat kahi ya sachaai se pehlu bachaaya to jaan rakho ke jo kuch tum karte ho Allah ko is ki khabar hai"
  4,136,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, imaan lao Allah par aur is ke rasool par aur is kitaab par jo Allah ne apne rasool par nazil ki hai aur har uss kitaab par jo is se pehlay woh nazil kar chuka hai jis ne Allah aur is ke mulaika aur is ki kitabon aur is ke Rasolo-n aur roz akhirat se kufar kya woh gumraahi mein bhatak kar bohat daur nikal gaya"
  4,137,"rahay woh log jo imaan laaye, phir kufar kya, phir imaan laaye, phir kufar kya, phir apne kufar mein barhatay chalay gay, to Allah hargiz un ko maaf nah kere ga aur nah kabhi unn ko raah raast dukhaay ga"
  4,138,aur jo munafiq ahal imaan ko chore kar kafiroon ko apna Rafeeq banatay hain inhen yeh musardah suna do ke unn ke liye dard naak saza tayyar hai
  4,139,kya yeh log izzat ki talab mein unn ke paas jatay hain? halaank izzat to saari ki saari Allah hi ke liye hai
  4,140,Allah iss kitaab mein tum ko pehlay hi hukum day chuka hai ke jahan tum suno ke Allah ki ayaat ke khilaaf kufar bakka ja raha hai aur a noon ka mazaq uraya ja raha hai wahan nah betho jab taq ke log kisi doosri baat mein nah lag jayen ab agar tum aisa karte ho to tum bhi unhi ki terhan ho yaqeen jano ke Allah mnafqon aur kafiroon ko jahannum mein aik jagah jama karne wala hai
  4,141,yeh munafiq tumahray maamla mein intzaar kar rahay hain ( ke oont kis karvat baithta hai ) agar Allah ki taraf se fatah tumhari hui to aa kar kahin ge ke kya hum tumahray sath nah thay? a gir kafiroon ka palla bhaari raha to unn se kahin ge ke kya hum tumahray khilaaf larnay par Qadir nah thay aur phir bhi hum ne tum ko musalmanoon se bachaaya? bas Allah hi tumahray aur un ke maamla ka faisla qayamat ke roz kere ga aur ( is faisla mein ) Allah ne kafiroon ke liye musalmanoon par ghalib anay ki hargiz koi Sabeel nahi rakhi hai
  4,142,yeh munafiq Allah ke sath dhoka baazi kar rahay hain halaank Dur haqeeqat Allah hi ne inhen dhoka mein daal rakha hai jab yeh namaz ke liye uthte hain tu kammsatehue mehez logon ko dikhaane ki khatir uthte hain aur khuda ko kam hi yaad karte hain
  4,143,kufar o imaan ke darmain dawaa_n doll hain nah poooray iss taraf hain nah poooray uss taraf jisay Allah ne bhatka diya ho is ke liye tum koi rasta nahi paskte
  4,144,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, mominon ko chore kar kafiroon ko apna Rafeeq nah banaao kya tum chahtay ho ke Allah ko apne khilaaf Sarih Hujjat day do ?"
  4,145,yaqeen jano ke munafiq jahannum ke sab se neechay tabqay mein jayen ge aur tum kisi ko unn ka madad gaar nah pao ge
  4,146,"Albata jo unn mein se Taib ho jayen o ray apne tarz amal ki islaah kar len aur Allah ka daman thaam len aur apne deen ko Allah ke liye khalis kar den, aisay log mominon ke sath hain aur Allah mominon ko zaroor ajar azeem ataa farmaiye ga"
  4,147,aakhir Allah ko kya pari hai ke tumhe khuwa makhuwa saza day agar tum shukar guzaar bande banay raho aur imaan ki rawish par chalo Allah bara qader daan hai aur sab ke haal se waaqif hai
  4,148,"Allah is ko pasand nahi karta ke aadmi bad goi par zabaan khole, ila yeh ke kisi par zulm kya gaya ho, aur Allah sab kuch suneney aur jan-nay wala hai"
  4,149,"( mazloom honay ki soorat mein agar chay tum par bad goi ka haq hai ) lekin agar tum zahir o batin mein bhalai hi kiye jao, ya kam az kam buraiee se Dur guzar karo, to Allah ki sift bhi yahi hai ke woh bara maaf karne wala hai halaank saza dainay par poori qudrat rakhta hai"
  4,150,"jo log Allah aur is ke Rasolo-n se kufar karte hain, aur chahtay hain ke Allah aur is ke Rasolo-n ke darmain tafreeq karen, aur kehte hain ke hum kisi ko manen ge aur kisi ko nah manen ge, aur kufar o imaan ke beech mein aik raah nikaalte ka iradah rakhtay hain"
  4,151,woh sab pakkay kafir hain aur aisay kafiroon ke liye hum ne woh saza muhayya kar rakhi hai jo inhen zaleel o khawar kar dainay wali hogi
  4,152,"bakhilaf is ke jo log Allah aur a seen ke tamam Rasolo-n ko manen, aur unn ke darmain tafreeq nah karen, unn ko hum zaroor unn ke ajar ataa karen ge, aur Allah bara dar guzar frmane wala aur reham karne wala hai"
  4,153,"yeh ahal kitaab agar aaj tum se mutalba kar rahay hain ke tum aasman se koi tehreer unn par nazil karao to iss se barh charh kar mujremana mutalbe yeh pehlay moose se kar chuke hain uss se to unhon ne kaha tha ke hamein khuda ko alania dikha do aur isi sar kashi ki wajah se yakayak inn par bijli toot pari thi phir unhon ne bichhre ko apna mabood bana liya, halaank yeh khuli khuli nishanain dekh chuke thay is par bhi hum ne inn se dar guzar kya hum ne moose ko Sarih farmaan ataa kya"
  4,154,aur inn logon par tor ko utha kar inn se ( uss farmaan ki itaat ka ) ehad liya hum ne inn ko hukum diya ke darwazay mein sajda raiz hotay hue daakhil hon hum ne inn se kaha ke sabt ka qanoon nah torro aur iss par inn se pukhta ehad liya
  4,155,"aakhir ka ray inn ki ehad shikni ki wajah se, aur is wajah se ke unhon ne Allah ki ayaat ko jhtlaya, aur mutadid payghambaroon ko na haq qatal kya, aur yahan taq kaha ke hamaray dil ghlafon mein mehfooz hain halaank Dur haqeeqat inn ki baatil parasti ke sabab se Allah ne inn ke dilon par thp_h laga diya hai aur isi wajah se yeh bohat kam imaan laatay hain"
  4,156,phir apne kufar mein itnay barhay ke maryam par sakht bohtan lagaya
  4,157,"aur khud kaha ke hum ne maseeh, eesa Ibn maryam, rasool Allah ko qatal kar diya hai halaank fi al waqea unhon ne nah is ko qatal kya nah saleeb par charhaya balkay maamla un ke liye mushtaba kar diya gaya aur jin logon ne is ke baray mein ikhtilaaf kya hai woh bhi darasal shak mein mubtala hain, un ke paas is maamla mein koi ilm nahi hai, mehez gumaan hi ki pairwi hai unhon ne maseeh ko yaqeen ke sath qatal nahi kya"
  4,158,"balkay Allah ne is ko apni taraf utha liya, Allah zabardast taaqat rakhnay wala aur hakeem hai"
  4,159,aur ahal kitaab mein se koi aisa nah hoga jo uss ki mout se pehlay is par imaan nah le aeye ga aur qayamat ke roz woh un par gawahi day ga
  4,160,"gharz inn yahodi ban jaane walon ke isi zalimana rawayya ki bana par, aur is bana par ke yeh bakasrat Allah ke rastay se roktay hain"
  4,161,"aur sood letay hain jis se inhen mana kya gaya tha, aur logon ke maal najaaiz tareeqon se khatay hain, hum ne bohat si woh pak cheeze un par haraam kar den jo pehlay un ke liye halal theen, aur jo log inn mein se kafir hain un ke liye hum ne dard naak azaab tayyar kar rakha hai"
  4,162,magar un mein jo log pukhta ilm rakhnay walay hain aur imandaar hain woh sab uss taleem par imaan laatay hain jo tumhari taraf nazil ki gayi hai aur jo tum se pehlay nazil ki gayi thi iss terhan ke imaan laane walay aur namaz o zkoh ki pabandi karne walay aur Allah aur roz aakhir par sacha aqeedah rakhnay walay logon ko hum zaroor ajar azeem ataa karen ge
  4,163,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! hum ne tumhari taraf usi terhan wahi bhaije hai jis terhan Nooh aur is ke baad ke payghambaroon ki taraf bhaije thi hum ne ibrahim, Ismael, ishaq, yaqoob aur aulaad yaqoob, eesa, ayub, Younis, haroon aur sulaiman ki taraf wahi bhaije hum ne DAWOD ko Zaboor di"
  4,164,hum ne unn Rasolo-n par bhi wahi nazil ki jin ka zikar hum iss se pehlay tum se kar chuke hain aur unn Rasolo-n par bhi jin ka zikar tum se nahi kya hum ne moose se iss terhan guftagu ki jis terhan guftagu ki jati hai
  4,165,yeh saaray rasool khush khaberi dainay walay aur darane walay bana kar beje gay thay taakay unn ko maboos kardainay ke baad logon ke paas Allah ke muqaabla mein koi Hujjat nah rahay aur Allah behar haal ghalib rehne wala aur hakeem o Dana hai
  4,166,"( log nahi mantay to nah manen ) magar Allah gawahi deta hai ke jo kuch uss ne tum par nazil kya hai apne ilm se nazil kya hai, aur iss par mulaika bhi gawah hain agarchay Allah ka gawah hona bilkul kifayat karta hai"
  4,167,jo log iss ko maan-ne se khud inkaar karte hain aur dosaron ko khuda ke rasta se roktay hain woh yaqeenan گمرا hi mein haq se bohat daur nikal gay hain
  4,168,"a seen terhan jin logon ne kufar o baghaawat ka tareeqa ikhtiyar kya aur zulm vstm par utar aeye Allah un ko hargiz maaf nah kere ga aur inhen koi rasta ,"
  4,169,bajuz jahannum ke rasta ke nah dukhaay ga jis mein woh hamesha rahen ge Allah ke liye yeh koi mushkil kaam nahi hai
  4,170,"logo! yeh rasool tumahray paas tumahray rab ki taraf se haq le kar agaya hai, imaan le aao, tumahray hi liye behtar hai, aur agar inkaar karte ho to jaan lau ke asmano aur zameen mein jo kuch hai sab Allah ka hai aur Allah Aleem bhi hai aur hakeem bhi"
  4,171,"ae ahal kitaab! apne deen mein ghallo nah karo aur Allah ki taraf haq ke siwa koi baat mansoob nah karo maseeh eesa Ibn maryam is ke siwa kuch nah tha ke Allah ka aik rasool tha aur aik farmaan tha jo Allah ne maryam ki taraf bheja aur aik rooh thi Allah ki taraf se ( jis ne maryam ke reham mein bacha ki shakal ikhtiyar ki ) pas tum Allah aur aُ seen ke Rasolo-n par imaan lao aur nah kaho ke"" teen"" hain baz aa jao, yeh tumahray hi liye behtar hai Allah to bas aik hi khuda hai woh baala tar hai is se ke koi is ka beta ho zameen aur asmano ki saari cheeze is ki Malik hain, aur un ki kifalat o khabar Gary ke liye bas wohi kaafi hai"
  4,172,"maseeh ne kabhi is baat ko aar nahi samgha ke woh Allah ka bandah ho, aur nah Maqarrab tareen farishtay iss ko apne liye aar samajte hain agar koi Allah ki bandagi ko apne liye aar samjhta hai aur taqqabur karta hai to aik waqt aeye ga jab Allah sab ko ghair kar apne samnay haazir kere ga"
  4,173,"uss waqt woh log jinhon ne imaan laa kar naik tarz amal ikhtiyar kya hai apne ajar poooray poooray payen ge aur Allah apne fazl se un ko mazeed ajar ataa farmaiye ga, aur jin logon ne bandagi ko aar samgha aur taqqabur kya hai unn ko Allah dard naak saza day ga aur Allah ke siwa jin jin ki sarparasti o مددگاری par woh bharosa rakhtay hain un mein se kisi ko bhi woh wahan nah payen ge"
  4,174,logo! tumahray rab ki taraf se tumahray paas Daleel roshan aa gayi hai aur hum ne tumhari taraf aisi roshni bhaij di hai jo tumhe saaf saaf rasta dikhaane wali hai
  4,175,ab jo log Allah ki baat maan len ge aur is ki panah dhunden ge un ko Allah apni rehmat aur apne fazl o karam ke daman mein le le ga aur apni taraf anay ka seedha rasta un ko dikha day ga
  4,176,"log tum se kalalah ke maamla mein Fatwa puchhte hain kaho Allah tumhe Fatwa deta hai agar koi shakhs be aulaad mar jaye aur is ki aik behan ho to woh is ke tarka mein se nisf paye gi, aur agar behan be aulaad marey to bhai is ka waris hoga agar maiyat ki waris do behnain hon to woh trke mein se do tahai ki haqdaar hon gi, aur agar kayi bhai behnain hon to aurton ka اkehra aur mardon ka dohra hissa hoga Allah tumahray liye ehkaam ki tozeeh karta hai taakay tum bhataktay nah phiro aur Allah har cheez ka ilm rakhta hai"
